{"tid":2461791,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"[ViuTV] ERROR主持 最後一屆口罩小姐選舉 星期一至五 21:30-22:30(8)","createTime":"2021-03-25T14:36:49.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-26T13:05:55.000Z","uid":313584,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"6b27601465b76c19743e72aa9f5318b79819be8c","tid":2461791,"uid":313584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T14:36:49.000Z","msg":"【口罩小姐】ViuTV最後一屆口罩小姐選舉3月22日播出！40強名單出爐 佳麗全程戴口罩保持神秘<br />\n<br />\n新冠肺炎疫情陰霾籠罩下，口罩成為市民不可或缺的日常生活用品。ViuTV亦因此舉行口罩小姐選舉，參賽佳麗全程戴口罩，與以往的選美比賽截然不同。今日ViuTV正式公布口罩小姐40強名單。為了保持神秘，佳麗除了戴口罩之外，在淘汰之前不會公開身份。節目將於3月22日開播，逢星期一至五晚上9點半播出。<br />\n<br />\n40位候選口罩小姐主要職業是模特兒、網紅和學生，不過亦有專業人士。而一眾佳麗的技能和興趣亦千奇百趣，有人以「含住水說話」作賣點，有人的興趣是「買口罩」，亦有身懷特別技能的參加者，如揸飛機。"},{"pid":"3364da712ca0289ff17bea7f7ee2fd3a1f83a519","tid":2461791,"uid":48854,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T16:19:16.000Z","msg":"肥腰最正<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6b31f169bffc918106ae4b91e484761b7e1673b","tid":2461791,"uid":289900,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T16:26:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmPq159UpQYuU1wWqH1vwtWWEka3xeJZamoc42QfVTf9xH?filename=yFfex4P.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyFfex4P.png&h=54fbea53&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmSt4UBbZx6TqUCPym7o9mkNbLvAnutQexSZ4kv4ZrnoZj?filename=VA5RAh9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVA5RAh9.jpg&h=4a755e58&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmZ4N4cP3kxyQmpmeKpDEtmHptgzCgr9DYjBTFcBgWdzNa?filename=fiEyODa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfiEyODa.jpg&h=75e6a264&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmRtvQwPSwo4SS5gqeeVq5nSLjZgqGgv5cPU6dtRxJsD6i?filename=2QL6pbw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2QL6pbw.jpg&h=1ce51528&s={SIZ